iterableData.description: We provide coverage for death/ injuries caused to individuals outside of your vehicle in accidents involving your car.
We also cover any damage/loss to third-party property.
Damages to your own car are not covered
This refers to any violation of traffic laws, such as driving without a valid license or driving under the influence of drugs, alcohol, etc.
